data.description: Your search is complete! Welcome to your new forever home. Just a short bike ride away from the Delaware Bay. Every evening you will get to enjoy the breath-taking sunsets from the comfort of your own home. This home sits on 1.55 Acres of land with a large portion of the yard cleared giving your imagination room to flourish. The backyard is fenced in for pets and or kids with a large patio. Inside the fenced area you will see an entrance to the basement. The finished basement has a large open area that adds ample amount of space to enjoy family time. The basement has two extra rooms with one being sized at 300 sq.ft. in addition to extra storage space. The flooring in the basement is only a year old. Upstairs you will find the master bed and bath and two standard sized rooms as well as additional full bath. This home is perfect for any family. This warm and inviting home has been well maintained by the current owner and is move in ready for the next. The home has Solar panels installed and are leased for $95 a month. Don't miss this opportunity to see this modern home in the beautiful and quiet area of Fortescue.
